  textLines:
  - text: Welcome to the combat tutorial, where you will learn the basic controls
      for combat
  - text: To use the basic attack, left mouse click or right trigger (controller).
  - text: In order to use the attack ability, right mouse click or right button (controller).
  - text: The clock icons in the top left corner signify your health, each equal
      2 hits.
  - text: Pickup last star to complete tutorial
